{"tid":2496241,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"45 歲李奧納多到底交過多少任女友？神人完整統計出來「總數竟比他的年齡還要多」！","createTime":"2021-04-19T16:23:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T03:33:38.000Z","uid":147522,"like":80,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"29c217783ef22fdc5516286c649b72407c80e8fa","tid":2496241,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T16:23:16.000Z","msg":"今年已經 45 歲的好萊塢巨星李奧納多狄卡皮歐（Leonardo DiCaprio）可以說是全球最知名的未婚演藝圈富裕名人，在剛於美國洛杉磯盛大舉辦完成的第 77 屆金球獎頒獎典禮上，主持人也大膽當面調侃李奧納多「永遠只交往 25 歲以下年輕妹子」的江湖傳說，讓這位奧斯卡影帝不禁露出尷尬笑容。不過你是否也會好奇，在李奧納多呼風喚雨、想要多少女人幾乎都可以得到的豐富情史上，他在過去 45 年究竟交往過多少女友呢？<br />\n<br />\n國外八卦網站「Who's Dated Who」就詳細列出了李奧納多自從 1993 年出道以來全部有紀錄過的緋聞女友名單，從英國傳奇超模凱特摩絲到一同共演電影《羅密歐與茱麗葉》的女主角 Claire Danes 全都聚集，同時還詳細標示出李奧納多與這些女性交往的年份時間表。<br />\n<br />\n如果標示上「Rumor」就是媒體之間爆出緋聞，但並未拍到李奧納多與女方一起親密合體的約會照片，你可能會驚訝李奧納多與「黑珍珠」娜歐蜜坎貝兒到布魯斯威利前妻黛咪摩爾，各式各樣不同個性和外型的女人都與他約會過。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWjkDv5uz5Ms8ZjiuGM4ojDewPKghH2jvUUFirH2Zacg3?filename=KtEB8B7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKtEB8B7.jpg&h=03debd31&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfHr54Ki5igGHPX6JmMa79THjqiw5BztPDBa9Peg1x5N3?filename=vbVhS3R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvbVhS3R.jpg&h=42719e48&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmf5YiT8JdRTvmUwmErhib4a1WPsXhJCshW1hmWgVpdhCb?filename=rzHTroS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrzHTroS.jpg&h=8ad359cf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXhB6S7STQF8WyDdf1YBqnkFzPjqtHvjmqeMScSf2gRfN?filename=DJuKx3U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDJuKx3U.jpg&h=2c1d9729&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeSrYv7oAJrHYUnkzgrr9oNDjyzHhS3jTboXZpTtzBkhM?filename=q5wkQQB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq5wkQQB.jpg&h=43e8bc03&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPih584YnkbnK1n5MjEn4LFPYojp89B3g47FjX9GXx7Ky?filename=Erjbc3X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FErjbc3X.jpg&h=2b7ee40c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTLzrqu6QQoxMHjxMr9VX9BTm9tqKxiDbf64ghYfJ9GrD?filename=GUkmAhj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGUkmAhj.png&h=0d9a85fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n要挑選出李奧納多演員名人生涯中最知名的一任女友，絕對非全球最會賺的超級名模吉賽兒邦臣（Gisele B&uuml;ndchen）莫屬。曾經差點與「吉娘娘」論及婚嫁的李奧納多一交往就是 6 年，這也是李奧納多演藝生涯中維持交往時間最長久的一段戀情。之後已經另嫁他人的吉賽兒邦臣回憶起這段戀情就直言：「與李奧納多失敗戀情，我痛苦到酒精麻痺自己」。<br />\n<br />\n從 1993 年一路數到現在交往的嫩模 Camila Morrone，李奧納多在演藝圈生涯就交往過總數多達 51 位名人女友！若是保守估計把謠傳的緋聞女友扣除，李奧納多真實交往過的女星和小模也有 32 位！尤其是近年來李奧納多都交往 25 歲以下的年輕女模，讓網友不禁笑說：「李奧納多自己都可以舉辦一場維多利亞的祕密大秀了！」亦可參考皮卡丘的年輕時代傳說：詹姆斯卡麥隆《鐵達尼號》最終選擇李奧納多是因為「他太帥了」，整棟女員工都偷跑來看他！"},{"pid":"ea8ac325efda9921b0ef972f77f421bba9b23d8d","tid":2496241,"uid":254453,"like":127,"dislike":5,"score":122,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T16:27:06.000Z","msg":"ca姐？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4abf46226dbd17d472ee1c45f6399b1d90c026c6","tid":2496241,"uid":301538,"like":88,"dislike":1,"score":87,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T16:31:13.000Z","msg":"早期個d高質好多，近年d女除左後生冇咩特別。宜家先知佢連Paris Hilton都食過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e7736c21d99772cdffb4ea2995e568806c04a42","tid":2496241,"uid":248670,"like":37,"dislike":2,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T16:43:09.000Z","msg":"Barbara Palvin應該唔係<br />\n佢話識dylan 之前空白成7年 睇到佢而家同dylan仲咁sweet 覺得呢7年等得好值"},{"pid":"41a84d7a2caf7415dc139ba6e729f443fd612717","tid":2496241,"uid":274500,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T04:23:40.000Z","msg":"fuck boy到<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/crowd.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/crowd.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d120d0ab2899e6d60f95f0bb7638800dc885c091","tid":2496241,"uid":147522